# Environment Configuration

Tambahkan konfigurasi berikut ke file `.env` Anda:

## Notification & WhatsApp Configuration

```env
# WhatsApp Integration via Fonnte.com
WHATSAPP_ENABLED=true
WHATSAPP_FONNTE_URL=https://api.fonnte.com/send
WHATSAPP_FONNTE_KEY=your_fonnte_api_key_here

# Database defaults
DB_CONNECTION=sqlite
DB_DATABASE=database/database.sqlite

# Mail configuration (optional for notifications)
MAIL_MAILER=smtp
MAIL_HOST=smtp.mailtrap.io
MAIL_PORT=465
MAIL_USERNAME=your_username
MAIL_PASSWORD=your_password
MAIL_ENCRYPTION=tls
MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=noreply@example.com
MAIL_FROM_NAME="${APP_NAME}"

# Application
APP_NAME="Haiti ITSM Dashboard"
APP_ENV=production
APP_DEBUG=false
APP_URL=http://localhost:8000
```

## Setup Langkah Demi Langkah

### 1. Copy Environment File

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

### 2. Generate Application Key

```bash
php artisan key:generate
```

### 3. Run Migrations

```bash
# Create database migrations
php artisan migrate

# Or if using fresh install
php artisan migrate:fresh --seed
```

### 4. Set Up WhatsApp Fonnte

```bash
# Get Fonnte API Key from https://dashboard.fonnte.com
# Edit .env dan tambahkan:
WHATSAPP_ENABLED=true
WHATSAPP_FONNTE_KEY=your_key_here
```

### 5. Compile Assets

```bash
npm run build

# Or for development:
npm run dev
```

### 6. Create Sample User for Testing

```bash
php artisan tinker

# Create test user with phone number
App\Models\User::create([
    'name' => 'Test User',
    'email' => 'test@example.com',
    'password' => bcrypt('password'),
    'phone_number' => '62812345678'
]);

# Get user and add role
$user = App\Models\User::first();
$user->assignRole('User');
```

### 7. Start Development Server

```bash
php artisan serve
```

Server akan berjalan di: http://localhost:8000

## Verifikasi Setup

### Test WhatsApp Connection

```bash
php artisan tinker

# Test send WhatsApp
$service = app(\App\Services\WhatsAppService::class);
$result = $service->send('62812345678', 'Test message dari aplikasi');
dd($result);
```

### Check Notifications Table

```bash
php artisan tinker

# View sent notifications
$notifications = \App\Models\Notification::where('whatsapp_sent', true)->get();
$notifications->each(fn($n) => dump([
    'title' => $n->title,
    'phone_sent' => $n->user->phone_number,
    'status' => $n->whatsapp_status
]));
```

## Features Checklist

### ✅ Implemented

- [x] Dashboard dengan statistik
- [x] Manajemen Tickets (CRUD)
- [x] Manajemen Assets (CRUD)
- [x] Manajemen Reservations (CRUD)
- [x] Notification System (Database + UI)
