### API Endpoints

```
# Notifications
GET    /api/notifications                  - List notifications
GET    /api/notifications/unread-count     - Get unread count
GET    /api/notifications/latest-unread    - Latest 5 unread
GET    /api/notifications/{id}             - View notification
PATCH  /api/notifications/{id}/mark-as-read
PATCH  /api/notifications/mark-all-as-read
DELETE /api/notifications/{id}             - Delete notification

# Tickets (Web)
GET    /tickets                - List
POST   /tickets                - Create
GET    /tickets/{id}           - View
PATCH  /tickets/{id}           - Update
DELETE /tickets/{id}           - Delete
POST   /tickets/{id}/comments  - Add comment

# Assets (Web)
GET    /assets                 - List
POST   /assets                 - Create
GET    /assets/{id}            - View
PATCH  /assets/{id}            - Update
DELETE /assets/{id}            - Delete

# Reservations (Web)
GET    /reservations           - List
POST   /reservations           - Create
GET    /reservations/{id}      - View
PATCH  /reservations/{id}      - Update
DELETE /reservations/{id}      - Delete
```

## Default Credentials

Jika menggunakan `migrate:fresh --seed`:

- Email: `admin@example.com`
- Password: `password`

## Troubleshooting

### WhatsApp Tidak Terkirim

1. Pastikan `WHATSAPP_ENABLED=true` di `.env`
2. Verifikasi Fonnte API Key benar
3. Check log: `tail -f storage/logs/laravel.log | grep whatsapp`
4. Pastikan user memiliki phone_number

### Notification Tidak Muncul

1. Check database: `php artisan tinker` → `\App\Models\Notification::latest()->first()`
2. Verifikasi API endpoint accessible: `curl http://localhost:8000/api/notifications/unread-count`
3. Check Chrome DevTools → Network tab untuk API calls

### Assets Tidak Muncul

1. Run: `npm run build`
2. Clear cache: `php artisan cache:clear`
3. Clear compiled views: `php artisan view:clear`

## Performance Tips

1. **Use Database Indexing**: Notifications table sudah indexed pada (user_id, is_read)
2. **Cache Unread Count**: Sidebar bell melakukan cache hit setiap 30 detik
3. **Queue WhatsApp**: Untuk production, gunakan queue:
   ```php
   dispatch(new SendWhatsAppJob($user, $message))->onQueue('default');
   ```
4. **Rate Limit**: Fonnte memiliki rate limit, cek dashboard untuk status

## Security

- ✅ Authentication via Laravel Breeze
- ✅ Authorization via Spatie Roles & Permissions
- ✅ CSRF Protection
- ✅ SQL Injection Protection (Eloquent ORM)
- ✅ XSS Protection (Blade templates)
- ✅ Password Hashing (bcrypt)
- ✅ Secure Headers

## Backup & Recovery

```bash
# Backup database
php artisan backup:run

# Export notifications
php artisan db:seed --class=NotificationSeeder
```
